cloud security posture management(CSPM)
=======================================

Ability of an organisation to detect,prevent,respond to threat.

CSPM tool allow org to view
1.cloud resources
2.misconfigurations
3.View change in resources
4.User involved with the change
5.Compliance requirements fullfillment.

Employing CSPM tools is first step to securing cloud infrastructure.

